column8: NDH shuttles electrons from NAD(P)H plastoquinone, via FMN and iron-sulfur (Fe-S) centers, to quinones in the photosynthetic chain and possibly in a chloroplast respiratory chain. Couples the redox reaction to proton translocation, and thus conserves the redox energy in a proton gradient
